---
title: Chorizo and Mozzarella Rigatoni with wilted spinach and rocket salad
description: This is a simple pasta dish featuring standout ingredients to make for a meal that's easy to assemble but still tastes great. Melted mozzarella and slightly spicy chorizo are only a few of the noteworthy elements in this easy weeknight meal.
